org.mini2Dx.core.collision

Interface QuadTreeAware

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    QuadTreeAwareCollisionBox, QuadTreeAwareCollisionCircle, QuadTreeAwareCollisionPoint, QuadTreeAwareCollisionPolygon, QuadTreeAwareObject

    public interface QuadTreeAware
    A common interface for objects that are aware of quad trees and as such can use QuadTreeSearchDirection.UPWARDS search.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      QuadTree getQuad()
      Returns the QuadTree where this object is located.
      void setQuad(QuadTree quadTree)
      Sets the QuadTree where this object is located.

    • Method Detail

      • setQuad

        void setQuad(QuadTree quadTree)
        Sets the QuadTree where this object is located. Automatically called by QuadTree.add(T) methods. NOTE: Internal use only.
        Parameters:
        quadTree - The QuadTree where this object is located.

      • getQuad

        QuadTree getQuad()
        Returns the QuadTree where this object is located. You can call this method in order to get the QuadTree on which you can do QuadTreeSearchDirection.UPWARDS search.
        Returns:
        QuadTree where this object is located.
